# Anomaly handling

Verification failures are tracked as issues in the project's issue tracker.
Each failure is triaged, assigned a severity, and linked to the affected requirement(s).

Resolution is verified by re-running the affected verification activity.

Failures of automated CI verification gates are treated as verification failures and are subject to the same anomaly handling process.
